I called a total of 9 times and not once did anyone offer a reason for why it's late or its location. I eventually go to the store around 1044pm thats around the time i actually get there. On the way the driver finally calls saying do you still want your pizza. I respond with i want a refund and he hangs up immediately. I get to the store asking to speak to the manager so they can call corporate so i can request my money to be returned in 24 hours and not 4 to 6 business days. It took them 2 hours to make and never deliver my order so in less than that time they can give me my money back. The manager proceeds to say we dont have a corporate. He states its on the website like its always been. After some more arguing he gives me the number. There was only 2 paying customers in the store the whole time. So they were not busy. To back track a lil, one of the times i called i asked to speak with a manager and they put me on hold for 10 min or maybe more. Everytime i order from this location there is a problem. Apparently the drivers are not allowed to get out thier cars when delivering pizza. They dont call to let you know they are downstairs.
